扎卡河在[[聖經|聖經]]中被称为雅博河<ref name="oxford">{{Cite book |url=http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/44650958 |title=The Oxford History of the Biblical World |last=Coogan |first=Michael David |publisher=[[牛津大學出版社|Oxford University Press]] |location=Oxford, UK; New York, USA |accessdate=2017-08-28 |year=2001 |isbn=9780195139372 |page=10 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829024153/http://www.worldcat.org/title/oxford-history-of-the-biblical-world/oclc/44650958 |archivedate=2017-08-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>（{{lang-he|יבוק}}，''Nahal Yabok''）。[[雅各_(舊約聖經)|雅各]]在离开[[哈兰_(土耳其)|哈兰]]前往[[圣地_(地区)|迦南]]的途中穿过了雅博河。它向西进入住棚谷，从那里穿过约旦河可以很容易地到达[[示劍|示劍]]，正如雅各最终所做的那样。圣经中的城市撒拉但和亚当也在山谷的谷口。

